OM versions netiek skartas.)"},            {MenuLangId::Lithuanian, "Taiso pseudo 64-bit bitset bug, kuris track-ina active friend/opponent slots. JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0 slots 32–59 nėra handle-inami teisingai; kai kurie friends/opponents gali nepasirodyti online. Tai pakeičia processing į per-byte bitset logic kaip JP1.1 / US1.1 / EU1.1 / KR1.0. (Tik JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0. Kitos ROM versions nepaveikiamos.)"},            {MenuLangId::Afrikaans, "Maak die pseudo 64-bit bitset bug reg wat active friend/opponent slots track. In JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0 word slots 32–59 nie reg handle nie; sommige friends/opponents mag nie online verskyn nie. Dit vervang processing met per-byte bitset logic soos in JP1.1 / US1.1 / EU1.1 / KR1.0. (Net JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0. Ander ROM versions word nie geraak nie.)"},            {MenuLangId::Irish, "Ceartaíonn sé pseudo 64-bit bitset bug a track-álann active friend/opponent slots. I JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0 ní handle-áiltear slots 32–59 i gceart; d'fhéadfadh roinnt friends/opponents gan a bheith le feiceáil online. Athraíonn sé processing go per-byte bitset logic mar atá i JP1.1 / US1.1 / EU1.1 / KR1.0. (JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0 amháin. Ní théann sé i bhfeidhm ar ROM versions eile.)"},            {MenuLangId::Assamese, "active friend/opponent slots track কৰা pseudo 64-bit bitset bug ঠিক কৰে। JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0-ত slots 32–59 সঠিকভাৱে handle নহয়; কিছুমান friends/opponents online দেখা নাযাব পাৰে। ই processing-টো JP1.1 / US1.1 / EU1.1 / KR1.0-ৰ দৰে per-byte bitset logic-লৈ সলনি কৰে। (কেৱল JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0। আন ROM versions প্ৰভাৱিত নহয়।)"},            {MenuLangId::Amharic, "active friend/opponent slotsን የሚከታተል pseudo 64-bit bitset bug ይጠግናል። JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0 ላይ slots 32–59 በትክክል handle አይደረጉም፤ አንዳንድ friends/opponents online ላይ ላይታዩ ይችላሉ።"},            {MenuLangId::Estonian, "Parandab pseudo 64-bit bitset bugi, mis jälgib active friend/opponent slots. JP1.0 / US1.0 / EU1.0 ei handle'i slots 32–59 õigesti; mõned friends/opponents ei pruugi