иот horizontal range check; со тоа се исправува shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Bulgarian, "Заменя последния Ice Wave hit/miss angle check с full 3D evaluation, но запазва оригиналния horizontal range check; така се поправя shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Belarusian, "Замяняе апошні Ice Wave hit/miss angle check на full 3D evaluation, але захоўвае арыгінальны horizontal range check; гэта выпраўляе shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Maltese, "Ibiddel l-aħħar Ice Wave hit/miss angle check għal full 3D evaluation, iżda jżomm l-horizontal range check oriġinali; b'hekk jirranġa shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Mongolian, "Сүүлийн Ice Wave hit/miss angle check-г full 3D evaluation болгож өөрчилнө, гэхдээ анхны horizontal range check-г хадгална; ингэснээр shadow freeze засагдана."},            {MenuLangId::Latvian, "Pēdējo Ice Wave hit/miss angle check maina uz full 3D evaluation, bet saglabā oriģinālo horizontal range check; tā tiek labots shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Lithuanian, "Paskutinį Ice Wave hit/miss angle check pakeičia į full 3D evaluation, bet išlaiko originalų horizontal range check; taip pataisomas shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Afrikaans, "Vervang die laaste Ice Wave hit/miss angle check met full 3D evaluation, maar behou die oorspronklike horizontal range check; dit maak shadow freeze reg."},            {MenuLangId::Irish, "Athraíonn sé an Ice Wave hit/miss angle check deireanach go full 3D evaluation, ach coinníonn sé an horizontal range check bunaidh; ceartaíonn sé seo shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Assamese, "শেষ Ice Wave hit/miss angle check-টো full 3D evaluation-লৈ সলনি কৰে, কিন্তু মূল horizontal range check ৰাখে; ইয়াৰ ফলত shadow freeze ঠিক হয়।"},            {MenuLangId::Amharic, "የመጨረሻውን Ice Wave hit/miss angle check ወደ full 3D evaluation ይቀይራል፣ ግን የመጀመሪያውን horizontal range check ይጠብቃል፤ በዚህ shadow freeze ይጠገናል።"},            {MenuLangId::Estonian, "Asendab viimase Ice Wave hit/miss angle checki full 3D evaluationiga, kuid säilitab algse horizontal range checki; see parandab shadow freeze'i."},            {MenuLangId::Kazakh, "Соңғы Ice Wave hit/miss angle check-ті full 3D evaluation-ға ауыстырады, бірақ бастапқы horizontal range check сақталады; осылай shadow freeze түзетіледі."},            {MenuLangId::Catalan, "Substitueix l'últim Ice Wave hit/miss angle check per full 3D evaluation, però conserva l'horizontal range check original; això corregeix shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Kyrgyz, "Акыркы Ice Wave hit/miss angle checkти full 3D evaluationга алмаштырат, бирок баштапкы horizontal range check сакталат; ушундайча shadow freeze оңдолот."},            {MenuLangId::Slovak, "Nahrádza posledný Ice Wave hit/miss angle check za full 3D evaluation, ale zachováva pôvodný horizontal range check; tým opravuje shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Slovenian, "Zadnji Ice Wave hit/miss angle check zamenja s full 3D evaluation, vendar ohrani prvotni horizontal range check; s tem popravi shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Zulu, "Ishintsha i-Ice Wave hit/miss angle check yokugcina ibe yi-full 3D evaluation, kodwa igcina i-horizontal range check yasekuqaleni; lokhu kulungisa i-shadow freeze."},            {MenuLangId::Basque, "Azken Ice Wave hit/miss angle check full 3D evaluation bihurtzen du, baina jatorrizko horizontal range check mantentzen du; horrela shadow freeze konpontzen da."},            {MenuLangId::Hebrew, "מחליף את Ice Wave hit/miss angle check האחרון ב-full 3D evaluation, אך שומר על horizontal range check המקורי; כך shadow freeze מתוקן."},

















































