Input alebo reWASD. Užitočné, ak assigned button zostane po pustení akoby stlačený. Pri priamom použití keyboard a mouse môže vypnutie mierne znížiť input latency."},            {MenuLangId::Slovenian, "Compatibility mode za zunanja controller→keyboard/mouse converter tools, kot so JoyToKey, Steam Input ali reWASD. Uporabno, če assigned button po spustu ostane kot pritisnjen. Pri neposredni uporabi keyboard in mouse lahko izklop rahlo zmanjša input latency."},            {MenuLangId::Zulu, "Compatibility mode yamathuluzi angaphandle e-controller→keyboard/mouse converter afana ne-JoyToKey, Steam Input noma reWASD. Iwusizo uma i-assigned button isala sengathi icindezelwe ngemva kokuyiyeka. Uma usebenzisa keyboard ne-mouse ngqo, ukuyicisha kunganciphisa kancane input latency."},            {MenuLangId::Basque, "Compatibility mode kanpoko controller→keyboard/mouse converter tools-entzat, adibidez JoyToKey, Steam Input edo reWASD. assigned button askatu ondoren sakatuta balego bezala geratzen bada erabilgarria. keyboard eta mouse zuzenean erabiltzen badituzu, itzaltzeak input latency pixka bat murriztu dezake."},            {MenuLangId::Hebrew, "Compatibility mode לכלי controller→keyboard/mouse converter חיצוניים כמו JoyToKey, Steam Input או reWASD. שימושי אם assigned button נשאר כאילו הוא לחוץ אחרי שחרור. אם משתמשים ישירות ב-keyboard ו-mouse, כיבוי יכול להפחית מעט input latency."},

















































