    {
        "labelMetroidScreenSyncDesc",
        {
            {MenuLangId::Japanese, "オフ: 同期なし (最小遅延ですが、表示がカクつくことがあります)。glFinish: 各フレームの描画完了を待つことで表示を滑らかにします。DwmFlush: Windowsコンポジターと同期して表示を滑らかにします (Windowsのみ)。画面がカクついたりちらついたりする場合は、glFinishまたはDwmFlushを試してください。早送り/スローモーション中は自動的に無効になります。"},
            {MenuLangId::German, "Aus: Keine Synchronisation (geringste Latenz, Anzeige kann ruckeln). glFinish: Glattere Anzeige durch Warten auf den Abschluss jedes Frames. DwmFlush: Synchronisation mit dem Windows-Compositor (nur Windows). Bei Ruckeln oder Flackern glFinish oder DwmFlush testen. Wird bei Vorspulen/Zeitlupe automatisch deaktiviert."},
            {MenuLangId::Spanish, "Desactivado: sin sincronización (mínima latencia, pero la imagen puede entrecortarse). glFinish: imagen más fluida esperando a que termine cada fotograma. DwmFlush: sincroniza con el compositor de Windows (solo Windows). Si hay tirones o parpadeos, prueba glFinish o DwmFlush. Se desactiva automáticamente en avance rápido/cámara lenta."},
            {MenuLangId::French, "Désactivé : pas de synchronisation (latence minimale, affichage parfois saccadé). glFinish : affichage plus fluide en attendant la fin de chaque image. DwmFlush : synchronise avec le compositeur Windows (Windows uniquement). En cas de saccades ou scintillement, essayez glFinish ou DwmFlush. Désactivé automatiquement en avance rapide/ralenti."},
            {MenuLangId::Italian, "Disattivato: nessuna sincronizzazione (latenza minima, ma l'immagine può scattare). glFinish: immagine più fluida attendendo il completamento di ogni frame. DwmFlush: sincronizza con il compositor Windows (solo Windows). In caso di scatti o sfarfallio, prova glFinish o DwmFlush. Disattivato automaticamente in avanzamento rapido/ralenti."},
            {MenuLangId::Dutch, "Uit: geen synchronisatie (laagste latentie, beeld kan haperen). glFinish: vloeiender beeld door te wachten op het einde van elk frame. DwmFlush: synchroniseert met de Windows-compositor (alleen Windows). Bij haperen of flikkeren, probeer glFinish of DwmFlush. Wordt automatisch uitgeschakeld bij vooruitspoelen/slow motion."},
            {MenuLangId::Portuguese, "Desativado: sem sincronização (latência mínima, mas a imagem pode falhar). glFinish: imagem mais fluida ao aguardar o fim de cada fotograma. DwmFlush: sincroniza com o compositor do Windows (apenas Windows). Se houver falhas ou cintilação, experimente glFinish ou DwmFlush. Desativa-se automaticamente em avanço rápido/câmara lenta."},
            {MenuLangId::Russian, "Выкл.: без синхронизации (минимальная задержка, но возможны рывки). glFinish: более плавное изображение за счёт ожидания завершения каждого кадра. DwmFlush: синхронизация с композитором Windows (только Windows). При рывках или мерцании попробуйте glFinish или DwmFlush. Автоматически отключается при ускорении/замедлении."},
            {MenuLangId::ChineseSimplified, "关闭：不同步（延迟最低，但画面可能卡顿）。glFinish：等待每帧绘制完成使画面更平滑。DwmFlush：与 Windows 合成器同步（仅 Windows）。若画面卡顿或闪烁，可尝试 glFinish 或 DwmFlush。快进/慢动作时自动禁用。"},
            {MenuLangId::ChineseTraditional, "關閉：不同步（延遲最低，但畫面可能卡頓）。glFinish：等待每幀繪製完成使畫面更平滑。DwmFlush：與 Windows 合成器同步（僅 Windows）。若畫面卡頓或閃爍，可嘗試 glFinish 或 DwmFlush。快進/慢動作時自動禁用。"},
            {MenuLangId::ChineseHongKong, "關閉：不同步（延遲最低，但畫面可能卡頓）。glFinish：等待每幀繪製完成使畫面更平滑。DwmFlush：與 Windows 合成器同步（僅 Windows）。若畫面卡頓或閃爍，可嘗試 glFinish 或 DwmFlush。快進/慢動作時自動禁用。"},
            {MenuLangId::Korean, "끔: 동기화 없음(최소 지연이지만 화면이 끊길 수 있음). glFinish: 각 프레임 렌더 완료를 기다려 화면을 부드럽게 함. DwmFlush: Windows 컴포지터와 동기화(Windows 전용). 화면이 끊기거나 깜빡이면 glFinish 또는 DwmFlush를 시도하세요. 빨리감기/슬로 모션 중에는 자동으로 꺼집니다."},
            {MenuLangId::Arabic, "إيقاف: بلا مزامنة (أقل تأخير، لكن العرض قد يتقطع). glFinish: عرض أنعم بانتظار اكتمال كل إطار. DwmFlush: يزامن مع مركّب Windows (Windows فقط). عند التقطيع أو الوميض، جرّب glFinish أو DwmFlush. يُعطَّل تلقائياً أثناء التقديم السريع/الحركة البطيئة."},
            {MenuLangId::Indonesian, "Mati: tanpa sinkronisasi (latensi minimum, tampilan bisa tersendat). glFinish: tampilan lebih halus dengan menunggu setiap frame selesai. DwmFlush: sinkron dengan compositor Windows (hanya Windows). Jika tersendat atau berkedip, coba glFinish atau DwmFlush. Otomatis nonaktif saat fast-forward/slow motion."},
            {MenuLangId::Ukrainian, "Вимк.: без синхронізації (мінімальна затримка, але можливі риви). glFinish: плавніше зображення через очікування завершення кожного кадру. DwmFlush: синхронізація з композитором Windows (лише Windows). При ривках або мерехтінні спробуйте glFinish або DwmFlush. Автоматично вимикається під час прискорення/уповільнення."},
            {MenuLangId::Greek, "Ανενεργό: χωρίς συγχρονισμό (ελάχιστη καθυστέρηση, αλλά η εικόνα μπορεί να τραβάει). glFinish: πιο ομαλή εικόνα περιμένοντας το τέλος κάθε καρέ. DwmFlush: συγχρονίζει με τον συνθέτη Windows (μόνο Windows). Σε τραβήγματα ή τρεμόπαιγμα, δοκιμάστε glFinish ή DwmFlush. Απενεργοποιείται αυτόματα σε fast-forward/slow motion."},
            {MenuLangId::Swedish, "Av: ingen synkronisering (lägst latens, bilden kan hacka). glFinish: mjukare bild genom att vänta på varje bildruta. DwmFlush: synkar med Windows compositor (endast Windows). Vid hackning eller flimmer, prova glFinish eller DwmFlush. Inaktiveras automatiskt vid snabbspolning/slow motion."},
            {MenuLangId::Thai, "ปิด: ไม่ซิงค์ (หน่วงต่ำสุด แต่ภาพอาจกระตุก) glFinish: ภาพลื่นขึ้นด้วยการรอแต่ละเฟรมเสร็จ DwmFlush: ซิงค์กับ compositor ของ Windows (เฉพาะ Windows) หากกระตุกหรือกระพริบ ลอง glFinish หรือ DwmFlush ปิดอัตโนมัติขณะ fast-forward/slow motion"},
            {MenuLangId::Czech, "Vyp: bez synchronizace (nejnižší latence, obraz může trhat). glFinish: plynulejší obraz čekáním na dokončení každého snímku. DwmFlush: synchronizace s compositor Windows (pouze Windows). Při trhání nebo blikání zkuste glFinish nebo DwmFlush. Automaticky vypnuto při rychlém posunu/zpomalení."},
            {MenuLangId::Danish, "Fra: ingen synkronisering (lavest latency, billedet kan hakke). glFinish: jævnere billede ved at vente på hver frame. DwmFlush: synkroniserer med Windows-compositor (kun Windows). Ved hak eller flimmer, prøv glFinish eller DwmFlush. Deaktiveres automatisk ved spoling frem/slow motion."},
            {MenuLangId::Turkish, "Kapalı: senkronizasyon yok (en düşük gecikme, görüntü takılabilir). glFinish: her kare tamamlanana kadar bekleyerek daha akıcı görüntü. DwmFlush: Windows compositor ile senkronize eder (yalnızca Windows). Takılma veya titreme varsa glFinish veya DwmFlush deneyin. Hızlı ileri/yavaş çekimde otomatik kapanır."},
            {MenuLangId::Norwegian, "Av: ingen synkronisering (lavest latency, bildet kan hakke). glFinish: jevnere bilde ved å vente på hver frame. DwmFlush: synkroniserer med Windows-compositor (kun Windows). Ved hakking eller flimring, prøv glFinish eller DwmFlush. Deaktiveres automatisk ved spoling frem/slow motion."},
            {MenuLangId::Hungarian, "Ki: nincs szinkronizáció (legalacsonyabb késleltetés, a kép akadozhat). glFinish: simább kép minden képkocka befejezésének várakozásával. DwmFlush: szinkronizál a Windows compositorral (csak Windows). Akadozásnál vagy villogásnál próbáld a glFinish-t vagy DwmFlush-t. Gyorsított/lelassított lejátszásnál automatikusan kikapcsol."},
            {MenuLangId::Finnish, "Pois: ei synkronointia (pienin viive, kuva voi pätkiä). glFinish: tasaisempi kuva odottamalla jokaisen ruudun valmistumista. DwmFlush: synkronoi Windows-compositorin kanssa (vain Windows). Pätkimisessä tai välkynnässä kokeile glFinish tai DwmFlush. Poistuu automaattisesti pikakelauksessa/hidastuksessa."},
            {MenuLangId::Vietnamese, "Tắt: không đồng bộ (độ trễ thấp nhất, hình có thể giật). glFinish: hình mượt hơn bằng cách chờ mỗi khung hoàn tất. DwmFlush: đồng bộ với compositor Windows (chỉ Windows). Nếu giật hoặc nhấp nháy, thử glFinish hoặc DwmFlush. Tự tắt khi tua nhanh/chậm."},
            {MenuLangId::Polish, "Wył.: brak synchronizacji (najniższe opóźnienie, obraz może szarpać). glFinish: płynniejszy obraz przez oczekiwanie na zakończenie każdej klatki. DwmFlush: synchronizacja z compositor Windows (tylko Windows). Przy szarpaniu lub migotaniu spróbuj glFinish lub DwmFlush. Automatycznie wyłączone przy przewijaniu/slow motion."},
            {MenuLangId::Romanian, "Oprit: fără sincronizare (latență minimă, imaginea poate sări). glFinish: imagine mai fluidă așteptând finalizarea fiecărui cadru. DwmFlush: sincronizează cu compositorul Windows (doar Windows). La sărituri sau pâlpâire, încercați glFinish sau DwmFlush. Se dezactivează automat la derulare rapidă/slow motion."},            {MenuLangId::Filipino, "Off: walang sync (pinakamababang latency, maaaring mag-stutter ang display). glFinish: mas makinis ang display sa paghihintay na matapos ang bawat frame. DwmFlush: naka-sync sa Windows compositor (Windows lang). Kapag nag-stutter o kumikislap, subukan ang glFinish o DwmFlush. Awtomatikong naka-disable habang fast-forward/slow motion."},            {MenuLangId::Swahili, "Off: hakuna sync (latency ndogo zaidi, display inaweza kukwama-kukwama). glFinish: display laini zaidi kwa kusubiri kila frame ikamilike. DwmFlush: husawazisha na Windows compositor (Windows pekee). Ikiwa kuna stutter au flicker, jaribu glFinish au DwmFlush. Huzima kiotomatiki wakati wa fast-forward/slow motion."},            {MenuLangId::Croatian, "Off: bez sinkronizacije (najniža latencija, prikaz može trzati). glFinish: glađi prikaz čekanjem da svaki frame završi. DwmFlush: sinkronizacija s Windows compositorom (samo Windows). Ako ima trzanja ili treperenja, probaj glFinish ili DwmFlush. Automatski se isključuje tijekom fast-forward/slow motion."},            {MenuLangId::Icelandic, "Off: engin samstilling (lægsta töf, skjárinn getur hikstað). glFinish: mýkri birting með því að bíða eftir að hver frame klárist. DwmFlush: samstillt við Windows compositor (aðeins Windows). Ef það er stutter eða flicker, prófaðu glFinish eða DwmFlush. Slökknar sjálfkrafa í fast-forward/slow motion."},            {MenuLangId::Hindi, "Off: कोई sync नहीं (न्यूनतम latency, display अटक सकता है)। glFinish: हर frame के समाप्त होने की प्रतीक्षा करके display अधिक smooth। DwmFlush: Windows compositor से sync (केवल Windows)। यदि stutter या flicker हो, तो glFinish या DwmFlush आज़माएँ। Fast-forward/slow motion के दौरान अपने-आप बंद।"},            {MenuLangId::Bengali, "Off: কোনো sync নেই (সর্বনিম্ন latency, display stutter করতে পারে)। glFinish: প্রতিটি frame শেষ হওয়া পর্যন্ত অপেক্ষা করে display মসৃণ করে। DwmFlush: Windows compositor-এর সাথে sync (শুধু Windows)। Stutter বা flicker হলে glFinish বা DwmFlush চেষ্টা করুন। Fast-forward/slow motion চলাকালে স্বয়ংক্রিয়ভাবে বন্ধ হয়।"},            {MenuLangId::Urdu, "Off: کوئی sync نہیں (سب سے کم latency، display stutter کر سکتا ہے)۔ glFinish: ہر frame کے ختم ہونے کا انتظار کر کے display زیادہ smooth کرتا ہے۔ DwmFlush: Windows compositor کے ساتھ sync (صرف Windows)۔ Stutter یا flicker ہو تو glFinish یا DwmFlush آزمائیں۔ Fast-forward/slow motion کے دوران خودکار طور پر بند ہو جاتا ہے۔"},            {MenuLangId::Punjabi, "Off: ਕੋਈ sync ਨਹੀਂ (ਸਭ ਤੋਂ ਘੱਟ latency, display stutter ਕਰ ਸਕਦਾ ਹੈ)। glFinish: ਹਰ frame ਦੇ ਮੁਕੰਮਲ ਹੋਣ ਦੀ ਉਡੀਕ ਕਰਕੇ display ਹੋਰ smooth ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ। DwmFlush: Windows compositor ਨਾਲ sync (ਕੇਵਲ Windows)। Stutter ਜਾਂ flicker ਹੋਵੇ ਤਾਂ glFinish ਜਾਂ DwmFlush ਅਜ਼ਮਾਓ। Fast-forward/slow motion ਦੌਰਾਨ ਆਪਣੇ ਆਪ ਬੰਦ ਹੋ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ।"},            {MenuLangId::Telugu, "Off: sync లేదు (అత్యల్ప latency, display stutter కావచ్చు). glFinish: ప్రతి frame పూర్తయ్యే వరకు వేచి display మరింత smoothగా చేస్తుంది. DwmFlush: Windows compositorతో sync (Windows మాత్రమే). Stutter లేదా flicker ఉంటే glFinish లేదా DwmFlush ప్రయత్నించండి. Fast-forward/slow motion సమయంలో ఆటోమేటిక్‌గా off అవుతుంది."},            {MenuLangId::Persian, "Off: بدون sync (کمترین latency، display ممکن است stutter کند). glFinish: با انتظار برای پایان هر frame، نمایش را نرم‌تر می‌کند. DwmFlush: sync با Windows compositor (فقط Windows). اگر stutter یا flicker دارید، glFinish یا DwmFlush را امتحان کنید. هنگام fast-forward/slow motion خودکار خاموش می‌شود."},            {MenuLangId::Malay, "Off: tiada sync (latency paling rendah, display mungkin stutter). glFinish: menunggu setiap frame selesai untuk display yang lebih smooth. DwmFlush: sync dengan Windows compositor (Windows sahaja). Jika stutter atau flicker berlaku, cuba glFinish atau DwmFlush. Dimatikan secara automatik semasa fast-forward/slow motion."},            {MenuLangId::Marathi, "Off: sync नाही (सर्वात कमी latency, display stutter होऊ शकतो). glFinish: प्रत्येक frame पूर्ण होईपर्यंत थांबून display अधिक smooth करते. DwmFlush: Windows compositor सोबत sync (फक्त Windows). Stutter किंवा flicker असल्यास glFinish किंवा DwmFlush वापरून पाहा. Fast-forward/slow motion दरम्यान आपोआप बंद होते."},            {MenuLangId::Tamil, "Off: sync இல்லை (குறைந்த latency, display stutter ஆகலாம்). glFinish: ஒவ்வொரு frame முடிவையும் காத்திருந்து display ஐ smooth ஆக்கும். DwmFlush: Windows compositor உடன் sync (Windows மட்டும்). Stutter அல்லது flicker இருந்தால் glFinish அல்லது DwmFlush முயற்சிக்கவும். Fast-forward/slow motion போது தானாக off ஆகும்."},            {MenuLangId::Gujarati, "Off: sync નથી (સૌથી ઓછી latency, display stutter થઈ શકે). glFinish: દરેક frame પૂર્ણ થાય ત્યાં સુધી રાહ જોઈ display ને વધુ smooth કરે છે. DwmFlush: Windows compositor સાથે sync (માત્ર Windows). Stutter અથવા flicker હોય તો glFinish અથવા DwmFlush અજમાવો. Fast-forward/slow motion દરમિયાન આપમેળે બંધ થાય છે."},            {MenuLangId::Kannada, "Off: sync ಇಲ್ಲ (ಅತ್ಯಂತ ಕಡಿಮೆ latency, display stutter ಆಗಬಹುದು). glFinish: ಪ್ರತಿಯೊಂದು frame ಮುಗಿಯುವವರೆಗೆ ಕಾಯುವುದರಿಂದ display ಇನ್ನಷ್ಟು smooth ಆಗುತ್ತದೆ. DwmFlush: Windows compositor ಜೊತೆ sync (Windows ಮಾತ್ರ). Stutter ಅಥವಾ flicker ಇದ್ದರೆ glFinish ಅಥವಾ DwmFlush ಪ್ರಯತ್ನಿಸಿ. Fast-forward/slow motion ಸಮಯದಲ್ಲಿ ಸ್ವಯಂಚಾಲಿತವಾಗಿ off ಆಗುತ್ತದೆ."},            {MenuLangId::Odia, "Off: sync ନାହିଁ (ସବୁଠୁ କମ୍ latency, display stutter ହୋଇପାରେ). glFinish: ପ୍ରତ୍ୟେକ frame ଶେଷ ହେଉଅବଧି ଅପେକ୍ଷା କରି display କୁ ଅଧିକ smooth କରେ. DwmFlush: Windows compositor ସହ sync (କେବଳ Windows). Stutter କିମ୍ବା flicker ଥିଲେ glFinish କିମ୍ବା DwmFlush ଚେଷ୍ଟା କରନ୍ତୁ. Fast-forward/slow motion ସମୟରେ ସ୍ୱୟଂଚାଳିତ ଭାବେ off ହୁଏ."},            {MenuLangId::Malayalam, "Off: sync ഇല്ല (കുറഞ്ഞ latency, display stutter ഉണ്ടാകാം). glFinish: ഓരോ frame പൂർത്തിയാകുന്നതുവരെ കാത്ത് display കൂടുതൽ smooth ആക്കുന്നു. DwmFlush: Windows compositor നോട് sync ചെയ്യുന്നു (Windows മാത്രം). Stutter അല്ലെങ്കിൽ flicker ഉണ്ടെങ്കിൽ glFinish അല്ലെങ്കിൽ DwmFlush ശ്രമിക്കുക. Fast-forward/slow motion സമയത്ത് സ്വയമേവ off ആകും."},            {MenuLangId::Burmese, "Off: sync မရှိ (latency အနည်းဆုံး၊ display stutter ဖြစ်နိုင်)။ glFinish: frame တစ်ခုချင်းစီ ပြီးဆုံးသည်အထိ စောင့်ပြီး display ကို ပို smooth စေသည်။ DwmFlush: Windows compositor နှင့် sync လုပ်သည် (Windows သာ)။ Stutter သို့မဟုတ် flicker ရှိပါက glFinish သို့မဟုတ် DwmFlush စမ်းပါ။ Fast-forward/slow motion အတွင်း အလိုအလျောက် off ဖြစ်သည်။"},            {MenuLangId::Uzbek, "Off: sync yoʻq (eng past latency, display stutter boʻlishi mumkin). glFinish: har frame tugaguncha kutib, displayʼni silliqroq qiladi. DwmFlush: Windows compositor bilan sync (faqat Windows). Stutter yoki flicker boʻlsa glFinish yoki DwmFlushʼni sinab koʻring. Fast-forward/slow motion paytida avtomatik off boʻladi."},            {MenuLangId::Azerbaijani, "Off: sync yoxdur (ən aşağı latency, display stutter ola bilər). glFinish: hər frame bitənə qədər gözləyərək display-i daha smooth edir. DwmFlush: Windows compositor ilə sync (yalnız Windows). Stutter və ya flicker varsa glFinish və ya DwmFlush sınayın. Fast-forward/slow motion zamanı avtomatik off olur."},            {MenuLangId::Nepali, "Off: sync छैन (सबैभन्दा कम latency, display stutter हुन सक्छ)। glFinish: प्रत्येक frame सकिएसम्म पर्खेर display लाई बढी smooth बनाउँछ। DwmFlush: Windows compositor सँग sync (Windows मात्र)। Stutter वा flicker भए glFinish वा DwmFlush प्रयास गर्नुहोस्। Fast-forward/slow motion बेला स्वचालित रूपमा off हुन्छ।"},            {MenuLangId::Sinhala, "Off: sync නැත (අඩුම latency, display stutter විය හැක). glFinish: සෑම frame එකක්ම අවසන් වන තෙක් රැඳී display වඩා smooth කරයි. DwmFlush: Windows compositor සමඟ sync (Windows පමණි). Stutter හෝ flicker තිබේ නම් glFinish හෝ DwmFlush උත්සාහ කරන්න. Fast-forward/slow motion අතර ස්වයංක්‍රීයව off වේ."},            {MenuLangId::Khmer, "Off: គ្មាន sync (latency ទាបបំផុត, អាចមាន display stutter)។ glFinish: រង់ចាំឱ្យ frame នីមួយៗបញ្ចប់ ដើម្បីធ្វើឱ្យ display smooth ជាងមុន។ DwmFlush: sync ជាមួយ Windows compositor (Windows ប៉ុណ្ណោះ)។ បើមាន stutter ឬ flicker សាកល្បង glFinish ឬ DwmFlush។ ពេល Fast-forward/slow motion នឹង off ស្វ័យប្រវត្តិ។"},            {MenuLangId::Lao, "Off: ບໍ່ມີ sync (latency ຕ່ຳສຸດ, ອາດມີ display stutter). glFinish: ລໍຖ້າໃຫ້ແຕ່ລະ frame ຈົບ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ display smooth ຂຶ້ນ. DwmFlush: sync ກັບ Windows compositor (Windows ເທົ່ານັ້ນ). ຖ້າມີ stutter ຫຼື flicker ລອງ glFinish ຫຼື DwmFlush. ໃນ Fast-forward/slow motion ຈະ off ອັດຕະໂນມັດ."},            {MenuLangId::Armenian, "Off: sync չկա (ամենացածր latency, display stutter հնարավոր է)։ glFinish: սպասում է յուրաքանչյուր frame-ի ավարտին՝ display-ը ավելի smooth դարձնելու համար։ DwmFlush: sync Windows compositor-ի հետ (միայն Windows)։ Եթե stutter կամ flicker կա, փորձեք glFinish կամ DwmFlush։ Fast-forward/slow motion-ի ժամանակ ավտոմատ off է լինում։"},            {MenuLangId::Albanian, "Off: pa sync (latency më i ulët, mund të ketë display stutter). glFinish: pret që çdo frame të përfundojë për ta bërë display më smooth. DwmFlush: sync me Windows compositor (vetëm Windows). Nëse ka stutter ose flicker, provoni glFinish ose DwmFlush. Gjatë Fast-forward/slow motion fiket automatikisht."},            {MenuLangId::Georgian, "Off: sync არაა (ყველაზე დაბალი latency, შესაძლოა display stutter). glFinish: ელოდება თითოეული frame-ის დასრულებას, რათა display უფრო smooth იყოს. DwmFlush: sync Windows compositor-თან (მხოლოდ Windows). თუ stutter ან flicker არის, სცადეთ glFinish ან DwmFlush. Fast-forward/slow motion-ის დროს ავტომატურად off ხდება."},            {MenuLangId::Bosnian, "Off: nema sync (najniži latency, moguć display stutter). glFinish: čeka da svaki frame završi da display bude smooth. DwmFlush: sync s Windows compositorom (samo Windows). Ako imate stutter ili flicker, probajte glFinish ili DwmFlush. Tokom Fast-forward/slow motion automatski se isključuje."},            {MenuLangId::Serbian, "Off: нема sync (најнижи latency, могућ display stutter). glFinish: чека да сваки frame заврши да display буде smooth. DwmFlush: sync са Windows compositor-ом (само Windows). Ако имате stutter или flicker, пробајте glFinish или DwmFlush. Током Fast-forward/slow motion аутоматски се искључује."},            {MenuLangId::Macedonian, "Off: нема sync (најнизок latency, можен display stutter). glFinish: чека секој frame да заврши за display да биде smooth. DwmFlush: sync со Windows compositor (само Windows). Ако имате stutter или flicker, пробајте glFinish или DwmFlush. За време на Fast-forward/slow motion автоматски се исклучува."},            {MenuLangId::Bulgarian, "Off: няма sync (най-нисък latency, възможен display stutter). glFinish: чака всеки frame да приключи, за да е display по-smooth. DwmFlush: sync с Windows compositor (само Windows). Ако имате stutter или flicker, пробвайте glFinish или DwmFlush. По време на Fast-forward/slow motion автоматично се изключва."},            {MenuLangId::Belarusian, "Off: sync няма (найніжэйшы latency, магчымы display stutter). glFinish: чакае завяршэння кожнага frame, каб display быў smooth. DwmFlush: sync з Windows compositor (толькі Windows). Калі ёсць stutter або flicker, паспрабуйце glFinish або DwmFlush. Падчас Fast-forward/slow motion аўтаматычна выключаецца."},            {MenuLangId::Maltese, "Off: l-ebda sync (l-inqas latency, jista' jkun hemm display stutter). glFinish: jistenna kull frame jispiċċa biex id-display ikun aktar smooth. DwmFlush: sync mal-Windows compositor (Windows biss). Jekk hemm stutter jew flicker, ipprova glFinish jew DwmFlush. Waqt Fast-forward/slow motion jitfi awtomatikament."},            {MenuLangId::Mongolian, "Off: sync байхгүй (хамгийн бага latency, display stutter гарч магадгүй). glFinish: display smooth байлгахын тулд frame бүр дуусахыг хүлээнэ. DwmFlush: Windows compositor-той sync хийнэ (зөвхөн Windows). Stutter эсвэл flicker байвал glFinish эсвэл DwmFlush туршина уу. Fast-forward/slow motion үед автоматаар унтарна."},            {MenuLangId::Latvian, "Off: nav sync (zemākais latency, iespējams display stutter). glFinish: gaida katra frame pabeigšanu, lai display būtu smooth. DwmFlush: sync ar Windows compositor (tikai Windows). Ja ir stutter vai flicker, mēģiniet glFinish vai DwmFlush. Fast-forward/slow motion laikā automātiski izslēdzas."},            {MenuLangId::Lithuanian, "Off: nėra sync (mažiausias latency, galimas display stutter). glFinish: laukia kiekvieno frame pabaigos, kad display būtų smooth. DwmFlush: sync su Windows compositor (tik Windows). Jei yra stutter arba flicker, pabandykite glFinish arba DwmFlush. Fast-forward/slow motion metu automatiškai išsijungia."},            {MenuLangId::Afrikaans, "Off: geen sync (laagste latency, moontlike display stutter). glFinish: wag vir elke frame om klaar te wees sodat display meer smooth is. DwmFlush: sync met Windows compositor (net Windows). As jy stutter of flicker het, probeer glFinish of DwmFlush. Tydens Fast-forward/slow motion word dit outomaties afgeskakel."},            {MenuLangId::Irish, "Off: gan sync (latency is ísle, display stutter féideartha). glFinish: fanann sé go mbeidh gach frame críochnaithe chun display a dhéanamh níos smooth. DwmFlush: sync le Windows compositor (Windows amháin). Má tá stutter nó flicker ann, bain triail as glFinish nó DwmFlush. Múchann sé go huathoibríoch le linn Fast-forward/slow motion."},            {MenuLangId::Assamese, "Off: sync নাই (সৰ্বনিম্ন latency, display stutter হ'ব পাৰে)। glFinish: display অধিক smooth কৰিবলৈ প্ৰতিটো frame শেষ হোৱালৈ অপেক্ষা কৰে। DwmFlush: Windows compositor-ৰ সৈতে sync কৰে (কেৱল Windows)। stutter বা flicker থাকিলে glFinish বা DwmFlush চেষ্টা কৰক। Fast-forward/slow motion সময়ত স্বয়ংক্ৰিয়ভাৱে বন্ধ হয়।"},            {MenuLangId::Amharic, "Off: sync የለም (ዝቅተኛ latency፣ display stutter ሊኖር ይችላል)። glFinish: display smooth ለማድረግ እያንዳንዱ frame እስኪጨርስ ይጠብቃል። DwmFlush: ከWindows compositor ጋር sync ያደርጋል።"},            {MenuLangId::Estonian, "Off: sync puudub (madalaim latency, võimalik display stutter). glFinish: ootab iga frame'i lõppu, et display oleks smooth. DwmFlush: sync Windows compositoriga (ainult Windows). Kui esineb stutter või flicker, proovi glFinishi või DwmFlushi. Fast-forward/slow motion ajal lülitub automaatselt välja."},            {MenuLangId::Kazakh, "Off: sync жоқ (ең төмен latency, display stutter болуы мүмкін). glFinish: display smooth болуы үшін әр frame аяқталғанын күтеді. DwmFlush: Windows compositor-ымен sync жасайды (тек Windows). stutter немесе flicker болса glFinish немесе DwmFlush көріңіз."},            {MenuLangId::Catalan, "Off: sense sync (latency mínima, possible display stutter). glFinish: espera que cada frame acabi perquè el display sigui més smooth. DwmFlush: sync amb el Windows compositor (només Windows). Si tens stutter o flicker, prova glFinish o DwmFlush."},            {MenuLangId::Kyrgyz, "Off: sync жок (эң төмөн latency, display stutter болушу мүмкүн). glFinish: display smooth болушу үчүн ар бир frame аякташын күтөт. DwmFlush: Windows compositor менен sync кылат (Windows гана). stutter же flicker болсо glFinish же DwmFlush көрүңүз."},            {MenuLangId::Slovak, "Off: bez sync (najnižšia latency, možný display stutter). glFinish: čaká na koniec každého frame, aby bol display smooth. DwmFlush: sync s Windows compositorom (iba Windows). Pri stutter alebo flicker skúste glFinish alebo DwmFlush."},            {MenuLangId::Slovenian, "Off: brez sync (najnižja latency, možen display stutter). glFinish: počaka na konec vsakega frame, da je display smooth. DwmFlush: sync z Windows compositorjem (samo Windows). Pri stutter ali flicker poskusite glFinish ali DwmFlush."},            {MenuLangId::Zulu, "Off: akukho sync (latency ephansi kakhulu, display stutter ingenzeka). glFinish: ilinda ukuphela kwe-frame ngayinye ukuze display ibe smooth. DwmFlush: sync ne-Windows compositor (Windows kuphela). Uma kukhona stutter noma flicker, zama glFinish noma DwmFlush."},            {MenuLangId::Basque, "Off: sync gabe (latency baxuena, display stutter posiblea). glFinish: frame bakoitza amaitu arte itxaroten du display smooth izateko. DwmFlush: Windows compositor-arekin sync egiten du (Windows bakarrik). stutter edo flicker badago, saiatu glFinish edo DwmFlush."},            {MenuLangId::Hebrew, "Off: ללא sync (latency הנמוך ביותר, display stutter אפשרי). glFinish: ממתין לסיום כל frame כדי שה-display יהיה smooth. DwmFlush: sync עם Windows compositor (Windows בלבד). אם יש stutter או flicker, נסה glFinish או DwmFlush."},

















































