            {MenuLangId::Ukrainian, "Генерує фронти натискання/відпускання на стороні емулятора та накладає їх на внутрішній стан вводу MPH до обробки дій гравця. Охоплює стрільбу, стрибок, зум і рух. Читає маски кнопок з поточного пресета керування; автоматично підтримує всі пресети (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Greek, "Δημιουργεί ακμές πίεσης/αφής στην πλευρά του εξομοιωτή και τις επικαλύπτει στην εσωτερική κατάσταση εισόδου MPH πριν την επεξεργασία ενεργειών παίκτη. Καλύπτει πυροβολισμό, άλμα, ζουμ και κίνηση. Διαβάζει μάσκες κουμπιών από το τρέχον preset ελέγχου· υποστηρίζει αυτόματα όλα τα presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Swedish, "Genererar tryck-/släppkanter på emulatorsidan och lägger dem över MPH:s interna ingångstillstånd före spelaråtgärdsbearbetning. Täcker skjutning, hopp, zoom och rörelse. Läser knappmasker från aktuell kontrollpreset; stöder automatiskt alla presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Thai, "สร้าง edge กด/ปล่อยฝั่งเอมูเลเตอร์และซ้อนบนสถานะอินพุตภายใน MPH ก่อนประมวลผลการกระทำของผู้เล่น ครอบคลุมยิง กระโดด ซูม และเคลื่อนที่ อ่านมาสก์ปุ่มจาก preset การควบคุมปัจจุบัน รองรับ preset ทั้งหมด (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) อัตโนมัติ"},
            {MenuLangId::Czech, "Generuje hrany stisku/uvolnění na straně emulátoru a překrývá je na interní stav vstupu MPH před zpracováním akcí hráče. Pokrývá střelbu, skok, zoom a pohyb. Čte masky tlačítek z aktuálního ovládacího presetu; automaticky podporuje všechny presety (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Danish, "Genererer tryk-/slipkanter på emulator-siden og lægger dem over MPH's interne inputtilstand før spillerhandlingsbehandling. Dækker skydning, spring, zoom og bevægelse. Læser knapmasker fra nuværende kontrolpreset; understøtter automatisk alle presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Turkish, "Emülatör tarafında basma/bırakma kenarları üretir ve oyuncu eylemi işlenmeden önce MPH dahili giriş durumunun üzerine bindirir. Ateş, zıplama, zoom ve hareketi kapsar. Düğme maskelerini mevcut kontrol preset atamasından okur; tüm presetleri (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) otomatik destekler."},
            {MenuLangId::Norwegian, "Genererer trykk-/slippkanter på emulatorsiden og legger dem over MPHs interne inngangstilstand før spillerhandlingsbehandling. Dekker skyting, hopp, zoom og bevegelse. Leser knappmasker fra gjeldende kontrollpreset; støtter automatisk alle presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Hungarian, "Nyomás/felengedés éleket generál az emulátor oldalán, és a játékos művelet feldolgozása előtt ráhelyezi az MPH belső bemeneti állapotára. Lefedi a lövést, ugrást, zoomot és mozgást. A gombmaszkokat az aktuális vezérlési preset hozzárendelésből olvassa; automatikusan támogat minden presetet (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Finnish, "Luo painallus/vapautusreunat emulaattoripuolella ja asettaa ne MPH:n sisäiseen syötetilaan ennen pelaajatoimien käsittelyä. Kattaa ampumisen, hypyn, zoomin ja liikkeen. Lukee painikemaskit nykyisestä ohjauspresetistä; tukee automaattisesti kaikkia presetejä (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Vietnamese, "Tạo cạnh nhấn/thả phía emulator và chồng lên trạng thái đầu vào nội bộ MPH trước khi xử lý hành động người chơi. Bao phủ bắn, nhảy, zoom và di chuyển. Đọc mặt nạ nút từ preset điều khiển hiện tại; tự hỗ trợ mọi preset (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Polish, "Generuje krawędzie naciśnięcia/zwolnienia po stronie emulatora i nakłada je na wewnętrzny stan wejścia MPH przed przetwarzaniem akcji gracza. Obejmuje strzelanie, skok, zoom i ruch. Czyta maski przycisków z bieżącego presetu sterowania; automatycznie obsługuje wszystkie presety (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},
            {MenuLangId::Romanian, "Generează fronturi apăsare/eliberare pe partea emulatorului și le suprapune stării interne de intrare MPH înainte de procesarea acțiunilor jucătorului. Acoperă foc, salt, zoom și mișcare. Citește măștile butoanelor din presetul de control curent; suportă automat toate preseturile (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},            {MenuLangId::Filipino, "Gumagawa ito ng press/release edges sa emulator side at ino-overlay ang mga ito sa internal input state ng MPH bago ang player-action processing. Sakop nito ang fire, talon, zoom, at movement. Binabasa ang button mask mula sa kasalukuyang control preset ng player, kaya awtomatikong supported ang lahat ng preset (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},            {MenuLangId::Swahili, "Hutengeneza press/release edges upande wa emulator na kuzi-overlay kwenye internal input state ya MPH kabla ya player-action processing. Inashughulikia fire, ruka, zoom, na movement. Button mask husomwa kutoka control preset ya sasa ya player, hivyo presets zote (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) zinaungwa mkono kiotomatiki."},            {MenuLangId::Croatian, "Generira press/release edgeove na strani emulatora i preklapa ih preko internog input statea MPH-a prije obrade player akcija. Uključuje fire, skok, zoom i movement. Čita button mask iz trenutačnog control preseta; automatski podržava sve presete (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},            {MenuLangId::Icelandic, "Býr til press/release edges emulator-megin og leggur þau yfir innra input state MPH áður en player-action vinnsla fer fram. Nær yfir fire, stökk, zoom og movement. Les button mask úr núverandi control preset; styður sjálfkrafa öll preset (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)."},            {MenuLangId::Hindi, "Emulator side पर press/release edges बनाता है और player-action processing से पहले उन्हें MPH के internal input state पर overlay करता है। Fire, कूद, zoom और movement शामिल हैं। वर्तमान control preset से button mask पढ़ता है; सभी presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) को अपने-आप support करता है।"},            {MenuLangId::Bengali, "Emulator side-এ press/release edges তৈরি করে এবং player-action processing-এর আগে এগুলো MPH-এর internal input state-এ overlay করে। Fire, লাফ, zoom ও movement কভার করে। বর্তমান control preset থেকে button mask পড়ে; সব preset (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) স্বয়ংক্রিয়ভাবে সমর্থন করে।"},            {MenuLangId::Urdu, "Emulator side پر press/release edges بناتا ہے اور player-action processing سے پہلے انہیں MPH کے internal input state پر overlay کرتا ہے۔ Fire، چھلانگ، zoom اور movement cover کرتا ہے۔ موجودہ control preset سے button mask پڑھتا ہے؛ تمام presets (Touch R/L، Dual R/L) کو خودکار طور پر support کرتا ہے۔"},            {MenuLangId::Punjabi, "Emulator side 'ਤੇ press/release edges ਬਣਾਉਂਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ player-action processing ਤੋਂ ਪਹਿਲਾਂ ਇਹਨਾਂ ਨੂੰ MPH ਦੇ internal input state 'ਤੇ overlay ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ। Fire, ਛਾਲ, zoom ਅਤੇ movement cover ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ। ਮੌਜੂਦਾ control preset ਤੋਂ button mask ਪੜ੍ਹਦਾ ਹੈ; ਸਾਰੇ presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ਨੂੰ ਆਪਣੇ ਆਪ support ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ।"},            {MenuLangId::Telugu, "Emulator sideలో press/release edgesను సృష్టించి player-action processingకు ముందు వాటిని MPH internal input stateపై overlay చేస్తుంది. Fire, దూకు, zoom మరియు movementను cover చేస్తుంది. ప్రస్తుత control presetనుంచి button mask చదువుతుంది; అన్ని presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)ను ఆటోమేటిక్‌గా support చేస్తుంది."},            {MenuLangId::Persian, "در سمت Emulator، press/release edges می‌سازد و پیش از player-action processing آنها را روی internal input state در MPH overlay می‌کند. Fire، پرش، zoom و movement را پوشش می‌دهد. button mask را از control preset فعلی می‌خواند؛ همه presetها (Touch R/L، Dual R/L) را خودکار support می‌کند."},            {MenuLangId::Malay, "Mencipta press/release edges di pihak emulator dan overlay ke atas internal input state MPH sebelum player-action processing. Merangkumi fire, lompat, zoom dan movement. Membaca button mask daripada control preset semasa; menyokong semua presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) secara automatik."},            {MenuLangId::Marathi, "Emulator side वर press/release edges तयार करते आणि player-action processing आधी त्यांना MPH च्या internal input state वर overlay करते. Fire, उडी, zoom आणि movement कव्हर करते. सध्याच्या control preset मधून button mask वाचते; सर्व presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) आपोआप support करते."},            {MenuLangId::Tamil, "Emulator side இல் press/release edges உருவாக்கி, player-action processing க்கு முன் அவற்றை MPH internal input state மீது overlay செய்கிறது. Fire, தாவல், zoom, movement ஐ cover செய்கிறது. தற்போதைய control preset இலிருந்து button mask வாசிக்கிறது; அனைத்து presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ஐ தானாக support செய்கிறது."},            {MenuLangId::Gujarati, "Emulator side પર press/release edges બનાવે છે અને player-action processing પહેલાં તેને MPH internal input state પર overlay કરે છે. Fire, કૂદકો, zoom અને movement કવર કરે છે. હાલના control preset માંથી button mask વાંચે છે; બધા presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) આપમેળે support કરે છે."},            {MenuLangId::Kannada, "Emulator side ನಲ್ಲಿ press/release edges ರಚಿಸಿ, player-action processing ಮೊದಲು ಅವನ್ನು MPH internal input state ಮೇಲೆ overlay ಮಾಡುತ್ತದೆ. Fire, ಜಿಗಿತ, zoom ಮತ್ತು movement ಅನ್ನು cover ಮಾಡುತ್ತದೆ. ಪ್ರಸ್ತುತ control preset ನಿಂದ button mask ಓದುತ್ತದೆ; ಎಲ್ಲಾ presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ಅನ್ನು ಸ್ವಯಂಚಾಲಿತವಾಗಿ support ಮಾಡುತ್ತದೆ."},            {MenuLangId::Odia, "Emulator side ରେ press/release edges ସୃଷ୍ଟି କରେ ଏବଂ player-action processing ପୂର୍ବରୁ ସେଗୁଡ଼ିକୁ MPH internal input state ଉପରେ overlay କରେ. Fire, ଲାଫ, zoom ଓ movement cover କରେ. ବର୍ତ୍ତମାନ control preset ରୁ button mask ପଢ଼େ; ସମସ୍ତ presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ସ୍ୱୟଂଚାଳିତ ଭାବେ support କରେ."},            {MenuLangId::Malayalam, "Emulator side ൽ press/release edges സൃഷ്ടിച്ച്, player-action processing ക്ക് മുമ്പ് അവ MPH internal input state ന് മുകളിൽ overlay ചെയ്യുന്നു. Fire, ചാട്ടം, zoom, movement cover ചെയ്യുന്നു. നിലവിലെ control preset ൽ നിന്ന് button mask വായിക്കുന്നു; എല്ലാ presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) സ്വയമേവ support ചെയ്യുന്നു."},            {MenuLangId::Burmese, "Emulator side တွင် press/release edges ဖန်တီးပြီး player-action processing မတိုင်မီ ၎င်းတို့ကို MPH internal input state ပေါ် overlay လုပ်သည်။ Fire, ခုန်, zoom, movement ကို cover လုပ်သည်။ လက်ရှိ control preset မှ button mask ကို ဖတ်ပြီး presets အားလုံး (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ကို အလိုအလျောက် support လုပ်သည်။"},            {MenuLangId::Uzbek, "Emulator sideʼda press/release edges yaratadi va player-action processingʼdan oldin ularni MPH internal input state ustiga overlay qiladi. Fire, sakrash, zoom va movementʼni qamrab oladi. Joriy control presetʼdan button maskʼni oʻqiydi; barcha presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L)ʼni avtomatik support qiladi."},            {MenuLangId::Azerbaijani, "Emulator side-də press/release edges yaradır və player-action processing-dən əvvəl onları MPH internal input state üstünə overlay edir. Fire, tullanma, zoom və movement əhatə olunur. Cari control preset-dən button mask oxuyur; bütün presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) avtomatik support olunur."},            {MenuLangId::Nepali, "Emulator side मा press/release edges सिर्जना गर्छ र player-action processing अघि तिनीहरूलाई MPH internal input state माथि overlay गर्छ। Fire, हामफाल, zoom र movement cover हुन्छ। हालको control preset बाट button mask पढ्छ; सबै presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) स्वचालित रूपमा support गर्छ।"},            {MenuLangId::Sinhala, "Emulator side හි press/release edges නිර්මාණය කර player-action processing පෙර ඒවා MPH internal input state මත overlay කරයි. Fire, පැනීම, zoom සහ movement cover කරයි. වත්මන් control preset වෙතින් button mask කියවයි; සියලු presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ස්වයංක්‍රීයව support කරයි."},            {MenuLangId::Khmer, "បង្កើត press/release edges ខាង emulator ហើយ overlay វាលើ MPH internal input state មុន player-action processing។ គ្របដណ្តប់ Fire, លោត, zoom និង movement។ អាន button mask ពី control preset បច្ចុប្បន្ន; support presets ទាំងអស់ (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ដោយស្វ័យប្រវត្តិ។"},            {MenuLangId::Lao, "ສ້າງ press/release edges ຝັ່ງ emulator ແລະ overlay ມັນເທິງ MPH internal input state ກ່ອນ player-action processing. ຄຸ້ມຄອງ Fire, ໂດດ, zoom ແລະ movement. ອ່ານ button mask ຈາກ control preset ປັດຈຸບັນ; support presets ທັງໝົດ (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ອັດຕະໂນມັດ."},            {MenuLangId::Armenian, "Emulator side-ում ստեղծում է press/release edges և դրանք overlay է անում MPH internal input state-ի վրա՝ player-action processing-ից առաջ։ Ընդգրկում է Fire, ցատկ, zoom և movement։ Կարդում է button mask-ը ընթացիկ control preset-ից․ բոլոր presets-ը (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ավտոմատ supported են։"},            {MenuLangId::Albanian, "Krijon press/release edges në anën e emulatorit dhe i overlay mbi MPH internal input state para player-action processing. Mbulon Fire, kërcim, zoom dhe movement. Lexon button mask nga control preset aktual; të gjitha presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) supported automatikisht."},            {MenuLangId::Georgian, "ქმნის press/release edges-ს emulator side-ზე და მათ overlay აკეთებს MPH internal input state-ზე player-action processing-მდე. ფარავს Fire, ნახტომი, zoom და movement-ს. კითხულობს button mask-ს მიმდინარე control preset-იდან; ყველა presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) ავტომატურად supported არის."},            {MenuLangId::Bosnian, "Stvara press/release edges na emulator side i overlayuje ih preko MPH internal input state prije player-action processing. Pokriva Fire, skok, zoom i movement. Čita button mask iz trenutnog control preseta; svi presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) su automatski supported."},            {MenuLangId::Serbian, "Ствара press/release edges на emulator side и overlay-ује их преко MPH internal input state пре player-action processing. Покрива Fire, скок, zoom и movement. Чита button mask из тренутног control preset-а; сви presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) су аутоматски supported."},            {MenuLangId::Macedonian, "Создава press/release edges на emulator side и ги overlay-ува врз MPH internal input state пред player-action processing. Ги покрива Fire, скок, zoom и movement. Чита button mask од тековниот control preset; сите presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) се автоматски supported."},            {MenuLangId::Bulgarian, "Създава press/release edges от emulator side и ги overlay-ва върху MPH internal input state преди player-action processing. Покрива Fire, скок, zoom и movement. Чете button mask от текущия control preset; всички presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) се supported автоматично."},            {MenuLangId::Belarusian, "Стварае press/release edges на emulator side і overlay-іць іх на MPH internal input state перад player-action processing. Пакрывае Fire, скачок, zoom і movement. Чытае button mask з бягучага control preset; усе presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) supported аўтаматычна."},            {MenuLangId::Maltese, "Joħloq press/release edges fuq emulator side u jagħmilhom overlay fuq MPH internal input state qabel player-action processing. Ikopri Fire, qabża, zoom u movement. Jaqra button mask mill-current control preset; il-presets kollha (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) huma supported awtomatikament."},            {MenuLangId::Mongolian, "Emulator side дээр press/release edges үүсгэж, player-action processing-оос өмнө MPH internal input state дээр overlay хийнэ. Fire, үсрэлт, zoom, movement-г хамарна. Одоогийн control preset-ээс button mask уншина; бүх presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) автоматаар supported."},            {MenuLangId::Latvian, "Izveido press/release edges emulator side un overlay-o tos uz MPH internal input state pirms player-action processing. Aptver Fire, lēciens, zoom un movement. Nolasa button mask no current control preset; visi presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) tiek supported automātiski."},            {MenuLangId::Lithuanian, "Sukuria press/release edges emulator side ir overlay-ina juos ant MPH internal input state prieš player-action processing. Apima Fire, šuolis, zoom ir movement. Skaito button mask iš current control preset; visi presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) automatiškai supported."},            {MenuLangId::Afrikaans, "Skep press/release edges aan emulator side en overlay dit op MPH internal input state voor player-action processing. Dek Fire, spring, zoom en movement. Lees button mask uit huidige control preset; alle presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) word outomaties supported."},            {MenuLangId::Irish, "Cruthaíonn sé press/release edges ar emulator side agus overlay-álann sé iad ar MPH internal input state roimh player-action processing. Clúdaíonn sé Fire, léim, zoom agus movement. Léann sé button mask ón current control preset; tá gach preset (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) supported go huathoibríoch."},            {MenuLangId::Assamese, "emulator side-ত press/release edges সৃষ্টি কৰি, player-action processing-ৰ আগতে MPH internal input state-ত overlay কৰে। Fire, জঁপিয়াওক, zoom আৰু movement আৱৰি ধৰে। current control preset-ৰ পৰা button mask পঢ়ে; সকলো presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) স্বয়ংক্ৰিয়ভাৱে supported।"},            {MenuLangId::Amharic, "emulator side ላይ press/release edges ይፈጥራል እና ከplayer-action processing በፊት በMPH internal input state ላይ overlay ያደርጋል። Fire, ዝላይ, zoom, movement ይሸፍናል።"},            {MenuLangId::Estonian, "Loob emulator side'is press/release edges ja overlay'ib need MPH internal input state'ile enne player-action processingut. Katab Fire, hüpe, zoom ja movement. Loeb button maski current control presetist; kõik presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) on automaatselt toetatud."},            {MenuLangId::Kazakh, "emulator side-та press/release edges жасап, player-action processing алдында MPH internal input state үстіне overlay етеді. Fire, секіру, zoom және movement қамтиды. button mask current control preset-тен оқылады; барлық presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) автоматты supported."},            {MenuLangId::Catalan, "Crea press/release edges a emulator side i els overlay sobre MPH internal input state abans del player-action processing. Cobreix Fire, salt, zoom i movement. Llegeix button mask del current control preset; tots els presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) són supported automàticament."},            {MenuLangId::Kyrgyz, "emulator sideта press/release edges жасап, player-action processing алдында MPH internal input state үстүнө overlay кылат. Fire, секирүү, zoom жана movement камтыйт. button mask current control presetтен окулат; бардык presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) автоматтык supported."},            {MenuLangId::Slovak, "Na emulator side vytvára press/release edges a overlayuje ich do MPH internal input state pred player-action processingom. Pokrýva Fire, skok, zoom a movement. button mask sa číta z current control preset; všetky presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) sú automaticky supported."},            {MenuLangId::Slovenian, "Na emulator side ustvari press/release edges in jih overlaya v MPH internal input state pred player-action processingom. Pokriva Fire, skok, zoom in movement. button mask se bere iz current control preset; vsi presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) so samodejno supported."},            {MenuLangId::Zulu, "Yakha press/release edges ku-emulator side bese i-overlay ku-MPH internal input state ngaphambi kwe-player-action processing. Ihlanganisa Fire, gxuma, zoom ne-movement. button mask ifundwa ku-current control preset; wonke ama-presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) asekelwa ngokuzenzakalela."},            {MenuLangId::Basque, "emulator side-n press/release edges sortzen ditu eta MPH internal input state gainean overlay egiten ditu player-action processing aurretik. Fire, jauzia, zoom eta movement estaltzen ditu. button mask current control preset-etik irakurtzen da; presets guztiak (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) automatikoki supported daude."},            {MenuLangId::Hebrew, "יוצר press/release edges בצד emulator ומבצע overlay על MPH internal input state לפני player-action processing. מכסה Fire, קפיצה, zoom ו-movement. button mask נקרא מתוך current control preset; כל ה-presets (Touch R/L, Dual R/L) supported אוטומטית."},

















































