jani, "enable olduqda ARM9 hook oyunun native weapon-equip logic-indən istifadə edir. disable olduqda compatibility testing üçün ənənəvi touch/menu simulation istifadə edilir."},            {MenuLangId::Nepali, "enable भए ARM9 hook ले खेलको native weapon-equip logic प्रयोग गर्छ। disable भए compatibility testing का लागि परम्परागत touch/menu simulation प्रयोग हुन्छ।"},            {MenuLangId::Sinhala, "enable නම් ARM9 hook ක්‍රීඩාවේ native weapon-equip logic භාවිතා කරයි. disable නම් compatibility testing සඳහා සාම්ප්‍රදායික touch/menu simulation භාවිතා වේ."},            {MenuLangId::Khmer, "បើ enable, ARM9 hook ប្រើ native weapon-equip logic របស់ហ្គេម។ បើ disable វានឹងប្រើ touch/menu simulation បែបប្រពៃណីសម្រាប់ compatibility testing។"},            {MenuLangId::Lao, "ຖ້າ enable, ARM9 hook ໃຊ້ native weapon-equip logic ຂອງເກມ. ຖ້າ disable ຈະໃຊ້ touch/menu simulation ແບບດັ້ງເດີມສຳລັບ compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Armenian, "Եթե enable է, ARM9 hook-ը օգտագործում է խաղի native weapon-equip logic-ը։ Եթե disable է, compatibility testing-ի համար օգտագործվում է ավանդական touch/menu simulation։"},            {MenuLangId::Albanian, "Nëse enable, ARM9 hook përdor native weapon-equip logic të lojës. Nëse disable, përdoret touch/menu simulation tradicional për compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Georgian, "თუ enable არის, ARM9 hook იყენებს თამაშის native weapon-equip logic-ს. თუ disable არის, compatibility testing-ისთვის გამოიყენება ტრადიციული touch/menu simulation."},            {MenuLangId::Bosnian, "Ako je enable, ARM9 hook koristi native weapon-equip logic igre. Ako je disable, koristi se tradicionalni touch/menu simulation za compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Serbian, "Ако је enable, ARM9 hook користи native weapon-equip logic игре. Ако је disable, користи се традиционални touch/menu simulation за compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Macedonian, "Ако е enable, ARM9 hook користи native weapon-equip logic на играта. Ако е disable, се користи традиционален touch/menu simulation за compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Bulgarian, "Ако е enable, ARM9 hook използва native weapon-equip logic на играта. Ако е disable, за compatibility testing се използва традиционна touch/menu simulation."},            {MenuLangId::Belarusian, "Калі enable, ARM9 hook выкарыстоўвае native weapon-equip logic гульні. Калі disable, для compatibility testing выкарыстоўваецца традыцыйны touch/menu simulation."},            {MenuLangId::Maltese, "Jekk enable, ARM9 hook juża n-native weapon-equip logic tal-logħba. Jekk disable, tintuża touch/menu simulation tradizzjonali għal compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Mongolian, "Enable үед ARM9 hook тоглоомын native weapon-equip logic-г ашиглана. Disable үед compatibility testing-д уламжлалт touch/menu simulation ашиглана."},            {MenuLangId::Latvian, "Ja enable, ARM9 hook izmanto spēles native weapon-equip logic. Ja disable, compatibility testing izmanto tradicionālo touch/menu simulation."},            {MenuLangId::Lithuanian, "Jei enable, ARM9 hook naudoja žaidimo native weapon-equip logic. Jei disable, compatibility testing naudoja tradicinę touch/menu simulation."},            {MenuLangId::Afrikaans, "As enable, gebruik ARM9 hook die spel se native weapon-equip logic. As disable, word tradisionele touch/menu simulation vir compatibility testing gebruik."},            {MenuLangId::Irish, "Má tá enable air, úsáideann ARM9 hook native weapon-equip logic an chluiche. Má tá disable air, úsáidtear touch/menu simulation traidisiúnta do compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Assamese, "Enable থাকিলে, ARM9 hook-এ গেমৰ native weapon-equip logic ব্যৱহাৰ কৰে। Disable থাকিলে, compatibility testing-ৰ বাবে পৰম্পৰাগত touch/menu simulation ব্যৱহাৰ হয়।"},            {MenuLangId::Amharic, "Enable ሲሆን ARM9 hook የጨዋታውን native weapon-equip logic ይጠቀማል። Disable ሲሆን ለcompatibility testing የtouch/menu simulation ይጠቀማል።"},            {MenuLangId::Estonian, "Kui enable, kasutab ARM9 hook mängu native weapon-equip logicut. Kui disable, kasutatakse compatibility testinguks traditsioonilist touch/menu simulationit."},            {MenuLangId::Kazakh, "Enable болса, ARM9 hook ойынның native weapon-equip logic қолданады. Disable болса, compatibility testing үшін дәстүрлі touch/menu simulation қолданылады."},            {MenuLangId::Catalan, "Si és enable, l'ARM9 hook utilitza la native weapon-equip logic del joc. Si és disable, s'utilitza touch/menu simulation tradicional per a compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Kyrgyz, "Enable болсо, ARM9 hook оюндагы native weapon-equip logic колдонот. Disable болсо, compatibility testing үчүн салттуу touch/menu simulation колдонулат."},            {MenuLangId::Slovak, "Ak je enable, ARM9 hook používa native weapon-equip logic hry. Ak je disable, používa sa tradičná touch/menu simulation pre compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Slovenian, "Če je enable, ARM9 hook uporablja native weapon-equip logic igre. Če je disable, se za compatibility testing uporablja tradicionalni touch/menu simulation."},            {MenuLangId::Zulu, "Uma ku-enable, i-ARM9 hook isebenzisa i-native weapon-equip logic yomdlalo. Uma ku-disable, kusetshenziswa i-touch/menu simulation yendabuko ye-compatibility testing."},            {MenuLangId::Basque, "Enable badago, ARM9 hook-ek jokoaren native weapon-equip logic erabiltzen du. Disable badago, compatibility testing-erako touch/menu simulation tradizionala erabiltzen da."},            {MenuLangId::Hebrew, "כאשר enable, ARM9 hook משתמש ב-native weapon-equip logic של המשחק. כאשר disable, נעשה שימוש ב-touch/menu simulation מסורתי עבור compatibility testing."},

















































