ge hook padaro fire-input helper result true ir natūraliai naudoja cooldown, ammo, projectile spawn, HUD ir SFX native path. Senasis metodas naudoja tradicinį DS input/immediate-edge synthesis."},            {MenuLangId::Afrikaans, "As enable, maak native biped fire edge hook die fire-input helper result true en gebruik natuurlik cooldown, ammo, projectile spawn, HUD en SFX native path. Die ou metode gebruik tradisionele DS input/immediate-edge synthesis."},            {MenuLangId::Irish, "Má tá enable air, déanann native biped fire edge hook fire-input helper result true agus úsáideann sé cooldown, ammo, projectile spawn, HUD agus SFX native path go nádúrtha. Úsáideann an seanmhodh DS input/immediate-edge synthesis traidisiúnta."},            {MenuLangId::Assamese, "Enable হ'লে native biped fire edge hook এ fire-input helper result true কৰে আৰু cooldown, ammo, projectile spawn, HUD, SFX native path স্বাভাৱিকভাৱে ব্যৱহাৰ কৰে। পুৰণি পদ্ধতিয়ে DS input/immediate-edge synthesis ব্যৱহাৰ কৰে।"},            {MenuLangId::Amharic, "Enable ሲሆን native biped fire edge hook የfire-input helper resultን true ያደርጋል፣ እና cooldown, ammo, projectile spawn, HUD, SFX native path በተፈጥሮ ይጠቀማል። አሮጌው ዘዴ የDS input/immediate-edge synthesis ይጠቀማል።"},            {MenuLangId::Estonian, "Kui enable, teeb native biped fire edge hook fire-input helper resulti true'ks ning kasutab loomulikult cooldowni, ammot, projectile spawn'i, HUDi ja SFX native pathi. Vana meetod kasutab traditsioonilist DS input/immediate-edge synthesisit."},            {MenuLangId::Kazakh, "Enable болса, native biped fire edge hook fire-input helper result мәнін true етеді және cooldown, ammo, projectile spawn, HUD, SFX native path табиғи түрде қолданады. Ескі әдіс DS input/immediate-edge synthesis қолданады."},            {MenuLangId::Catalan, "Si és enable, el native biped fire edge hook fa true el fire-input helper result i utilitza naturalment cooldown, ammo, projectile spawn, HUD i SFX native path. El mètode antic utilitza